citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T18:24:37.000Z","msg":"你辜負咗包皮對你嘅期望"},{"pid":"cff2d8b8b3b68f136d19a35eb53469d3edec2b28","tid":989051,"uid":8648,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T18:39:22.000Z","msg":"笠住個紙杯去朋友生日會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeb02dc0b1f83a44ec5c72bd2467c8082c5bdeaa","tid":989051,"uid":195438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T18:42:44.000Z","msg":"其實點解要割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係過長，但係反到出嚟洗咪得"},{"pid":"e002ef2ad49969a3c63d580159dd89abffc2f0fa","tid":989051,"uid":66253,"like":56,"dislike":1,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T18:43:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c816800020a3d0618818b709d8446cc6aa0f567","tid":989051,"uid":232286,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T18:56:46.000Z","msg":"細個醫生話到青春期塊皮就會自然反到出嚟所以冇割<br />\n但一直去到十五六歲仲未反到<br />\n我覺得割包皮好恐怖<br />\n好驚俾醫生發現反唔出嚟要割<br />\n所以連續幾年健康檢查都唔去<br />\n<br />\n最後嗰時忍痛喺廁所用梘液潤滑慢慢反出嚟<br />\n忍住痛反咗成粒鐘先反到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果反完之後又反唔唔返上去紮住個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個頭紮到變成紫色<br />\n又搞咗一輪先反返上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但自從嗰次之後每日沖涼都順手反下佢<br />\n慢慢塊皮就反鬆咗<br />\n到依家一扯就自動反落嚟<br />\n可能無塊皮紮住<br />\n條撚可以繼續生長<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n總算無辜負我塊皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4805712ef52173df84e54be73a33b7d49e4d8498","tid":989051,"uid":80072,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T23:35:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 細個唔識嘢，幼稚園嗰陣有同學笠住個杯喺j，一陣痾尿時佢除開，見到好多黑色嘢，唔肯定係毛定咩，太細個冇印像，但肯定係一pat黑色，嗰陣以為佢喺條j度種蠶豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嗰陣又咁啱要種一棵，<br />\n<br />\n到而家廿幾年後我都唔知我嗰日見到啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a4a156f7f1781e6bfb288335e06910b085e7dcf","tid":989051,"uid":10195,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T23:50:48.000Z","msg":"識割更係暑假先割啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰年中一試下自己反，點知隔硬黎反到<br />\n但勒撚到個龍頭缺氧紫撚哂咁，call左入急症<br />\n之後醫生同我反番落黎，卜左下年暑假做手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自始有種覺得長大了嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"233aef4bfdd3fc82272e99278df2777f8fbc3b4d","tid":989051,"uid":66252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4805712ef52173df84e54be73a33b7d49e4d8498","tid":989051,"uid":80072,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T23:35:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 細個唔識嘢，幼稚園嗰陣有同學笠住個杯喺j，一陣痾尿時佢除開，見到好多黑色嘢，唔肯定係毛定咩，太細個冇印像，但肯定係一pat黑色，嗰陣以為佢喺條j度種蠶豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嗰陣又咁啱要種一棵，<br />\n<br />\n到而家廿幾年後我都唔知我嗰日見到啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T00:02:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好核突"},{"pid":"257d5dd2ad2870681ec57022d35af16a9d076bc3","tid":989051,"uid":66252,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a4a156f7f1781e6bfb288335e06910b085e7dcf","tid":989051,"uid":10195,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T23:50:48.000Z","msg":"識割更係暑假先割啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰年中一試下自己反，點知隔硬黎反到<br />\n但勒撚到個龍頭缺氧紫撚哂咁，call左入急症<br />\n之後醫生同我反番落黎，卜左下年暑假做手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自始有種覺得長大了嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T00:03:09.