<br />\n仲記得個陣入醫院訓病床同格離床位個男仔傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢同我一樣都係等割包皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個陣呀媽都算係咁 專登等我放暑假先帶我去割 所以我全程都係屋企著大人衫當裙咁著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗番起頭一個星期番到屋企屙尿痛到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c4e2ec0afa0aaabf98157661246a93789b62226","tid":989051,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T04:57:02.000Z","msg":"暑假先割啦梗係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df4245180ba08805b1b5e59dc8972259c7f8a25a","tid":989051,"uid":13914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ae8e6bdccac34b774c195783f2a91562ca2be1f2","tid":989051,"uid":30171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"47049e4830548fdd15b443558686c25f78bbfe9d","tid":989051,"uid":13914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T04:25:36.000Z","msg":"記得老母去M記買珍寶SIZE汽水然後洗乾淨個杯, 笠落JJ度不知幾有自豪感, 女同學眼甘甘咁望住"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T04:30:08.000Z","msg":"佢哋見到你條吸管仔做咩要篤住個大紙杯噤行啫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T04:59:03.000Z","msg":"佢地淨係睇到褲入面有座珠穆朗瑪峰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7140bbdee6fe1a93a4ee2a2474ac5dc50458643","tid":989051,"uid":209432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb559f514aee9aad909e9205a21a06d0895d1753","tid":989051,"uid":69098,"like":1099,"dislike":4,"score":1095,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T14:45:09.000Z","msg":"包皮以為你會生到咁長<br />\n點知你令佢失望<br />\n仲要割咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:06:54.000Z","msg":"恨鐵不成鋼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2943aed8a37be35e9764f94a08f356ffe143c862","tid":989051,"uid":27432,"like":0,"di