\n慢慢塊皮就反鬆咗<br />\n到依家一扯就自動反落嚟<br />\n可能無塊皮紮住<br />\n條撚可以繼續生長<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n總算無辜負我塊皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:59:46.000Z","msg":"實好多鳩屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 第一次反皮，成個圈都鳩屎"},{"pid":"a69f2f870877c7504e2a27363091e1e57327df79","tid":989051,"uid":175032,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"baf4b2be14e172958b1421ca4e8d03ad39d86254","tid":989051,"uid":27432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7853aeb994c5b6a41fea75a9d68932ef8571428a","tid":989051,"uid":175032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2943aed8a37be35e9764f94a08f356ffe143c862","tid":989051,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:08:16.000Z","msg":"其實做乜9要割包皮<br />\n正常大過就會出返黎<br />\n到時你想包返住都難"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:53:44.000Z","msg":"積鳩屎會發炎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:56:16.000Z","msg":"ON9, 想當年積左十幾年鳩屎都無發過炎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T06:05:28.000Z","msg":"你條牙簽仔爛撚咗緊係唔發炎喇<br />\n你咪撚自己on9拎黎同正常人比喇屌你老母"},{"pid":"49f37bd439112f41e3d298a3c40839064ee325e7","tid":989051,"uid":27432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a69f2f870877c7504e2a27363091e1e57327df79","tid":989051,"uid":175032,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"baf4b2be14e172958b1421ca4e8d03ad39d86254","tid":989051,"uid":27432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7853aeb994c5b6a41fea75a9d68932ef8571428a","tid":989051,"uid":175032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:53:44.000Z","msg":"積鳩屎會發炎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:56:16.000Z","msg":"ON9, 想當年積左十幾年鳩屎都無發過炎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T06:05:28.000Z","msg":"你條牙簽仔爛撚咗緊係唔發炎喇<br />\n你咪撚自己on9拎黎同正常人比喇屌你老母"